Check mirros for clearance on your right
when safe, pull over safely and come to a complete stop
turn on hazard lights
pull emergency break
open trunk
get out of car
pull out spare tire, take out wrench, take out jack
place jack underneath the chassis 
raise car by turning jack clockwise
once flat tire is off the ground, stop raising car
loosen lug nuts with wrench by turning lug nuts counter clockwise
take out flat tire
appropriately place tire on the axle
tighten lug nuts with wrench by turning clockwise
loosen jack by turning counter clockwise
once jack has completely retracted, remove from underneath the car
put jack back into designated trunck slot
place flat tire into trunk
get into car on driver side
turn off hazard lights
turn on car
signal left and safely merge onto road
watch out for pot holes!
